2026-02-13: Project start
================================================================
Goal: Subject/device-agnostic single-channel EEG sleep stage classifier for in-ear earbuds.
Data: 17 datasets, ~2,295 subjects, ~2.68M epochs, 5 device types, 128Hz, 30s epochs.

Prior work (abandoned):
- SincNet + Transformer: kappa 0.822 single-dataset, 0.64 multi-dataset ceiling
- CPC pretraining: no benefit over supervised
- Dual-branch CNN + BiGRU end-to-end: kappa 0.730 (11ds), 0.707 (17ds)
- Root cause: CNN encodes absolute amplitude (device-specific), not relative

