## Literature reviews (02-15, 02-17)
Reviewed ~30 repos/papers. All foundation models (EEGPT 10M, BIOT 3.3M, BENDR 15M,
LaBraM 5.8-369M, REVE 69-408M) performed worse on sleep with 5-200x our params.
Key insight: domain-specific inductive biases (AASM bands, CRF, BiGRU temporal context)
beat massive pretraining for single-channel sleep staging. Nothing borrowable.

