## Bugs fixed during this session
1. fp16 overflow (val_loss NaN, epoch 24): spec_decoder/wave_decoder outputs overflow fp16
   (~65k max) after sufficient training. Fix: .float() cast before MSE in _shared_step.
   Was causing EarlyStopping (check_finite=True) to kill training at epoch 24/50.
