## 2026-02-28: Per-branch diagnostic and spectral_only breakthrough

### Per-branch kNN diagnostic (eval_branches.py)
Sliced 640d encoder embeddings into 5x128d branches, ran kNN on each independently.
Critical finding: CNN branches carry ~zero N1 info (N1 F1 < 0.08), spectral branch best (N1 F1=0.252).
Fusion HURTS N1: fused 640d N1 F1=0.197 < spectral alone (0.252).

### Branch experiments (4 variants tested)
| Variant | test_kappa | test_f1 | delta_k | delta_f1 |
|---------|-----------|---------|---------|----------|
| bigru256 baseline | 0.757 | 0.763 | — | — |
| branch_weights | 0.753 | 0.764 | -0.004 | +0.001 |
| branch_gru | 0.756 | 0.763 | -0.001 | +0.000 |
| per_stage_heads | 0.753 | 0.761 | -0.004 | -0.002 |
| **spectral_only** | **0.762** | **0.770** | **+0.005** | **+0.007** |

### spectral_only: new best model
- Architecture: BiGRU+CRF on 256d (spectral+STFT only), dropping 384d CNN branches
- N1 F1 mean: 0.443 vs 0.418 (+0.025 across 17 datasets, wins 12/17)
- Headband devices: kappa +0.043, Forehead: +0.138
- Root cause: CNN embeddings are device-specific (waveform morphology), spectral features are device-invariant
- Checkpoint: checkpoints/sleep_model/spectral_only/epoch=5-val_kappa=0.770.ckpt

### spec_n1aux: spectral_only + N1AuxFeatures (NEW BEST)
N1AuxFeatures: downstream-only module (24K params) combining:
1. Static spectral features: spectral entropy, peak frequency, alpha-theta crossover
2. Sub-epoch dynamics: 3-segment band powers, slopes, alpha variance (24 features -> MLP -> 32d)
3. Augmented STFT: 2-layer transformer on STFT patches (vs encoder's 1-layer) -> 32d
Total: 64d concatenated with 256d spectral_only before GRU

Results:
- test_kappa=0.763, test_F1=0.773, test_acc=0.778
- Per-class F1: W=0.931, N1=0.520, N2=0.821, N3=0.746, REM=0.844
- Delta vs bigru256: +0.006 kappa, +0.010 F1, N1 +0.019, N3 +0.012, REM +0.011
- Delta vs spectral_only: +0.001 kappa, +0.003 F1
- Best epoch: 4 (val_kappa=0.7745), early stopped at epoch 14
- Checkpoint: checkpoints/sleep_model/spec_n1aux/epoch=4-val_kappa=0.774.ckpt

