Training instability: loss diverged after epoch 11 (1.5 -> 30+), metrics crashed.
Early stopping restored best checkpoint (epoch 5, val_f1_macro=0.778).
F1-monitoring selected epoch 5 vs kappa-monitoring epoch 9 -- different checkpoint selection.

Verdict: F1 monitoring is a wash. Selected checkpoint trades N2/N3 precision for slight
N1/REM gain. Training instability may be coincidental or related to different stopping dynamics.
Current best remains attn_pool (kappa-monitored).

