2026-03-01: Final model training (--exp-name final)
================================================================
Root cause of training collapse identified: AttentionPool softmax saturation at epoch 12.
Both runs with AttentionPool (attn_pool, f1_baseline) collapsed identically at epoch 12.
Baseline without AttentionPool never collapsed.

Fix: Removed AttentionPool class, reverted STFT to mean pooling.
Reverted monitoring from val_f1_macro to val_kappa.

Final model: spectral+STFT mean pooled (256d) -> BiGRU(384) -> shared head (768->128->5) + CRF
Training: 16 epochs, stable throughout, no collapse. Best val_kappa=0.774 at epoch 11.
Checkpoint: checkpoints/sleep_model/final/epoch=11-val_kappa=0.774.ckpt

Test results (335 subjects, 17 datasets):
  kappa=0.768, F1=0.777, acc=0.832
  W=0.937, N1=0.530, N2=0.823, N3=0.751, REM=0.844

Delta vs gru384 (pre-simplification best):
  kappa: -0.004 (expected from N1Aux removal)
  F1: -0.002
  N1 F1: -0.007

Architecture is now locked and simplified. Project complete.
